Name:    kremotecontrol 
Summary: KDE frontend for your remote controls 
Version: 17.08.3
Release: 19%{?dist}

# Automatically converted from old format: GPLv2+ - review is highly recommended.
License: GPL-2.0-or-later
URL:     http://utils.kde.org/projects/%{name}
